Looking at Trinity's hand like it might bite him, Scrat shakes his 
head at Windlord's question, his hand moving closer to Trinity's.

He yelps as his hand touches her claw, spinning around and trying to 
dig into the leaves, managing to get part of his head in, his 
trembling rear sticking up.
